  "title": "API Proposal: Every refining widget should expose `widget.on('refine')`",
  "body": "Every refinement widget instance should be an EventEmitter and so we would be able to:\n\n``` js\nvar categories =   instantsearch.widgets.menu({\n  container: '#categories',\n  facetName: 'categories',\n  limit: 10,\n  rootClass: 'list-unstyled',\n  template: require('./templates/category.html')\n});\n\ncategories.on('refine', function(newValue, previousValue) {\n  // do whatever you want here, like scrolling to some specific place or top.\n});\n\nsearch.addWidget(categories);\n```\n\n@algolia/javascript ?\n",
